{"tid":467172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東亞病夫】民航機不斷收到失踪幻影戰機求救訊號，但台灣軍方收不到！","createTime":"2017-11-13T09:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T18:12:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9b62fc265d0ec305cc471990e0f6278cb49970f7","tid":467172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171113/57452596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57452596&d=%2FYMK0%2FgWmQ5%2F85T3GOZOdU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4c3ae316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57452596&h=b3fb136e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171113/57452596</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510550508_c3fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510550508_c3fb.jpg&h=e927b2ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣空軍499聯隊一架由上尉何子雨所駕駛的單座2000-5型幻影戰機，執行夜間訓練時，突然在基隆北北東90海浬失蹤，台國防部立即發動海空兵力搜救，但迄今1星期仍無所獲。一名曾任空軍試飛官的李姓教官在facebook提到，連續2天在國際警戒波道聽到了「幻影」緊急定位發報器的訊號，懷疑跟何子雨有關。<br />\n<br />\n曾任空軍試飛官及駐日武官、現職民航機師的李文玉，昨日再度聽到「幻影」訊號！他說：「約10幾秒，可惜持續不長，不久後我們就被交到福岡的手上了。」他並指出，其實從「幻影」失蹤的消息傳開後，就陸續有民航機師反映，在基隆外海及M750航路附近截獲121.5的求救訊號，想必國軍搜救機艦也有所悉，甚至今早5點多仍有同事接獲訊號，「只是外海風驟浪急，要在如此廣袤的區域進行仔細的方格搜索着實不易。」<br />\n<br />\n李文玉上周五（10日）曾在fb提及，「上午7時多由台北飛往日本途中，爬升約三萬六千呎時，在國際警戒波道聽到了『幻影』緊急定位發報器的訊號，當時雖然已離開台北區管中心，而且或許超出了幻象機（幻影戰機）失蹤的海域，我們還是通知了福岡區管席，或許能在渺茫的機遇裏抓住希望的游絲。」<br />\n<br />\n何子雨妻子昨日也在李文玉的貼文下留言，「根據目前軍方回報給我們的消息，並沒有收到這些訊號，民航機收得到，但軍方收不到，有甚麼可能性呢？還是有更確切的地點呢？我們心急如焚，今天已經第6天了，拜託大家！」<br />\n<br />\n李文玉也解釋，「民航機監聽的，是VHF頻段121.5MHz的國際通用警戒波道，軍方雖然主要使用UHF頻段，但也有涵蓋VHF的守聽能力。不過聽見訊號不見得就能定位成功，還得視搜救機艦有否配備適當標定裝備。」「因高度幾乎達4萬呎，反推回去可能的地面發射範圍，勢必非常廣。」<br />\n<br />\n何子雨妻續問：「有辦法有更確切的相關座標嗎？」「我們該怎麼辦？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510550509_397a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510550509_397a.jpg&h=b08b7452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510550510_fd2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510550510_fd2d.jpg&h=ed65a879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510550512_6a2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510550512_6a2e.jpg&h=df040bcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be677ad547c96ad6c4901dc3c70a95bde16a0219","tid":467172,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"不如叫前香港皇家輔助空軍去啦<br />\n<br />\n香港一隊輔助空軍負責晒成個南海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gfs.gov.hk/Document/graphics/imgbgd/tc/aboutusc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gfs.gov.hk%2FDocument%2Fgraphics%2Fimgbgd%2Ftc%2Faboutusc.gif&h=d29068ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"343708ff418da1151336783a8bcf842db4147ccd","tid":467172,"uid":135891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如叫前香港皇家輔助空軍去啦<br />\n<br />\n香港一隊輔助空軍負責晒成個南海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gfs.gov.hk/Document/graphics/imgbgd/tc/aboutusc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gfs.gov.hk%2FDocument%2Fgraphics%2Fimgbgd%2Ftc%2Faboutusc.gif&h=d29068ff&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次十號風球gfs都出咗公海救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62a8dad71b7b6b8ece05de654d7e69b91fc9125","tid":467